data.description: Finally something to see! A lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence with a versatile Finished Room Over Garage (F.R.O.G) in the desirable location of China Grove, NC. This property offers a welcoming front porch, perfect for enjoying tranquil mornings, as well as a covered back porch for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Inside, the master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, providing ample storage space for your convenience. The F.R.O.G offers flexibility, making it an excellent choice for a home office or entertainment area. With a driveway leading to a garage, parking is hassle-free. Positioned for easy access to Highway 152, this home is an excellent opportunity for families and commuters seeking both comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this charming property your own in China Grove, NC. Schedule your viewing today!
